cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper focuses on developing a robust detection algorithm based on deep convolutional neural networks for parking management systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper involves the implementation and testing of the algorithm, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of deep learning techniques also suggests the possibility of the paper being categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves image analysis, which could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
